ity policy. This book will be suitable for academics and students interested in political violence, terrorism, geopolitics and risk, as well as for practitioners and experts working in the security industries"--cProvided by publisher.  a43 0aTerrorismxPrevention. 0aInternal security. 0aNational security. 0aWar on Terrorism, 2001-2009.1 aMythen, Gabe,eauthor. 0aNew directions in critical criminology ;v7.  aHV 6431 W347 2015c1hUAHS-Bi0162035181302  aHV 6431 W347 2015wLCc1i0162035181302d11/30/2015e11/20/2015lON_SHELFmUAHSSn1p$150.00rYsYtBOOKu11/19/201401ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no2004058541bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/317149310